{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require menus to be available in hard copy",
        "additional_details": "We believe that to have only QR code menus makes society less inclusive for all. It can be confusing not only dietary wise but also QR codes could have malware or expose you to scams",
        "background": "We are concerned that many people don't have devices to scan QR codes or have sufficient signal especially in rural areas. Some of us are also blind or disabled and can never use a QR code menu. There should always be a physical menu available. ",
